* '''[[1973 in literature|1974]]:''' No award given{{efn|group=notes|name=1974award|The fiction jury had unanimously recommended the 1974 award to [[Thomas Pynchon]]'s ''[[Gravity's Rainbow]]'', but the Pulitzer board, which has sole discretion for awarding the prize, made no award.&lt;ref name=&quot;controversies&quot; /&gt;}}
** ''[[Gravity's Rainbow]]'' by [[Thomas Pynchon]]
